      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it is in absolutely incredible shape. It drives like a total dream and looks even better. I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make the next owner so happy. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all!",
