    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours-level condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system for razor-sharp throttle response. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally perfect, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings for optimal lateral rigidity. This vehicle has undergone a comprehensive technical inspection: rod bearing service is documented, and valve clearances have been shimmed to factory specifications. Finished in Carbon Black with impeccable paint depth and zero oxidation, this is a mechanically flawless example of BMW\u2019s finest engineering.",
