      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, finished in a deep, lustrous paint that remains free of swirls, rock chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is original with factory-perfect gaps. Inside, the cabin retains its original 'new car' scent; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear, bolstering is firm, and the high-tech dashboard remains pristine without a single scratch on the displays or trim. Mechanically, it is flawless. I have maintained a comprehensive binder of every service performed exclusively at the authorized dealership, including a recent major inspection and full synthetic fluid flush. The tires are near-new, the alloys are free of curb rash, and the undercarriage is exceptionally clean. This is a rare opportunity to own a turnkey, investment-quality example that requires absolutely nothing but a new owner who appreciates perfection.",
